    "body": "The [code to get work area size](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/ui/gfx/screen_win.cc&sq=package:chromium&q=GetDisplay&type=cs&l=26) is implemented in Chromium, and as far as I can see it just returns the work area size returned by win32 API, not sure why it is not correct.\n"
